org.apache.flink.types

类 MapValue<K extends Value,V extends Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.types.MapValue<K,V>
  • 类型参数:
    K - Type of the map's key element.
    V - Type of the map's value element.
    所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, Map<K,V>, IOReadableWritable, Value

    @Public
public abstract class MapValue<K extends Value,V extends Value>
extends Object
implements Value, Map<K,V>
    Generic map base type for PACT programs that implements the Value and Map interfaces. The MapValue encapsulates a Java HashMap object.
    另请参阅:
    Value, Map, HashMap, 序列化表格

    • 嵌套类概要

      • 从接口继承的嵌套类/接口 java.util.Map

    • 构造器概要

      构造器 
      构造器和说明
      MapValue()
      Initializes the encapsulated map with an empty HashMap.
      MapValue(Map<K,V> map)
      Initializes the encapsulated map with a HashMap filled with all entries of the provided map.

      • MapValue

        参数:
        map - Map holding all entries with which the new encapsulated map is filled.
